import React from 'react'
import { Navbar, Container, Nav, Link } from 'react-bootstrap'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import './card.css'


export default function NavBar() {
    return (

        <>
            <Navbar bg="dark" data-bs-theme="dark"  >
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Brand href="#home" ><Link to="/movies">Home</Link></Navbar.Brand>
                    <Nav className="me-auto">
                        <Nav.Link > <Link to="/movies">Movies</Link></Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link><Link to="/">Series</Link></Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link><Link to="/anime">Anime</Link></Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>

        </>
    )
}
